過隔離車廂/下站落車 再等下一架</blockquote><br />\n鬼叫我地搭火車地鐵同人迫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4424a6f1b74b90c4cb14968f5d1cc7c8ce80e5e","tid":422224,"uid":151343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:10:06.000Z","msg":"好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb0e6bf0500151b3522ee77486f9f7c30be0250","tid":422224,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:15:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同意<br />\n成日都遇到呢啲人 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過:<br />\n坐隔離個阿姐吟佛經 <br />\n同3個打完波個頭仲滴緊水嘅中學生逼 汗味臭到<br />\n同肥臭毒撚逼<br />\n同痴線佬同一車廂<br />\n火車啲位無分得好清楚 有個肥阿叔仲要格硬攝埋黎<br />\n<br />\n通常我會過隔離車廂/下站落車 再等下一架</blockquote><br />\n鬼叫我地搭火車地鐵同人迫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係話我比幾蚊搭車就要求頭等服務<br />\n我覺得基本尊重起碼要有 同埋己所不欲 勿施於人<br />\n就算自己揸車 都想人細力啲關門 呢啲就係互相尊重<br />\n<br />\n如果要揀 我通常放工都搭巴士 地鐵太恐怖"},{"pid":"8171764869cd9b1b3c42d23ac669b83d4d282e94","tid":422224,"uid":11601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:48:19.000Z","msg":"隔住個moon都...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ade56a80722ba982a89081b6ffe0c6048417ff3","tid":422224,"uid":69599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:51:21.000Z","msg":"手動fliter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ac8e805abc6d04cee26499f1cf10cae7e1d44e","tid":422224,"uid":96406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T10:20:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同意<br />\n成日都遇到呢啲人 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過:<br />\n坐隔離個阿姐吟佛經 <br />\n同3個打完波個頭仲滴緊水嘅中學生逼 汗味臭到<br />\n同肥臭毒撚逼<br />\n同痴線佬同一車廂<br />\n火車啲位無分得好清楚 有個肥阿叔仲要格硬攝埋黎<br />\n<br />\n通常我會過隔離車廂/下站落車 再等下一架</blockquote><br />\n鬼叫我地搭火車地鐵同人迫<img src=\"/asset